item.description:
As you may or may not know, Sen. Rand Paul of KY is making a major speech at the RNC in Tampa this coming Wednesday night. We'll be hosting a Tampa Convention Watch Party at the Nashua Victory office. It should be a great opportunity to see some folks we haven't seen since primary season and of course, eat some free food. We'll kick things off about 6:00pm and will catch the Senator's speech on streaming coverage in the office.

That's this Wednesday, August 29th at 6:00pm-??

at the Nashua Victory Office-- 427 Amherst St, Unit #R-4A

Please let me know that you can make it so I can make sure we have plenty to eat (I will do my best to have something besides pizza :D).
item.name: Rand Paul Liberty Watch Party
